and they were placed on the van.

33
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:19,840
- 我来探望我姐妹 - 我跟你说了
- I've come to see my sister. - I've told you already,

34
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:22,080
一次只能有一位访客
just one visitor at a time.

35
