with her brother.

93
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:07,760
什么小插曲
What kind of scene?

94
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:11,240
她兄弟很难对付 让她很不安
An ugly one which left her very disturbed.

95
00:04:11,320 --> 00:04:13,480
他走之前还打了护士
He struck a nurse before leaving.

96
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,760
他叫什么
What's his name?

97
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:16,897
他叫斯蒂芬・博蒙特
Eh, it was Stephen Beaumont,

98
00:04:16,898 --> 00:04:17,720
法定近亲
he's the official next of kin.

99
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:19,338
是他送她来的
Did he bring her in?

100
00:04:19,339 --> 00:04:21,560
不 她自己坐救护车来的
No, she was on her own in the ambulance.

101
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:23,600
- 她现在在哪儿 - 在旁边的房间
- Where is she now? - Er, in a side room.

102
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:25,640
所以她跟那些老人一样都吃了同一种药
So, she ate the same poison as the old people?

103
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:27,280
是的 但因为她更年轻强壮
Yeah, but she's younger and fitter,

104
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:29,800
所以情况比较乐观
so her body's better able to deal with it.

105
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:31,920
这不能解释它是怎么到这儿来的 不是吗
It doesn't explain how it got there, does it?

106
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:34,980
她刚稳定下来 别跟她说话
She's through there.Don't try and talk to her.

107
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:42,000
你觉得是她干的吗
Do you think she did it?

108
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:43,434
先毒死十四名老人
Poisoned 14 old people

109
00:04:43,435 --> 00:04:45,240
然后假装用一样的方式自杀
and then tried to kill herself the same way?

110
00:04:45,320 --> 00:04:46,400
不是
No.

111
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:50,440
事实上是用鸦片类止痛
Given the fact that it was an opiate-based pain relief,

112
00:04:50,520 --> 00:04:53,420
我认为她偷了哈瑞特・斯通的药
I think she was stealing Harriet Stone's medication.

113
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:59,800
安全地回到了吗啡姐的怀抱
Safely back in the arms of Sister Morphine.

114
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:02,302
"亲爱的斯蒂芬 学校..."
"Dear Stephen, how is..."

115
00:05:02,303 --> 00:05:03,040
"亲爱的斯蒂芬"
"Dear Stephen."

116
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,280
"学校怎么样"
"How is school?"

117
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:06,840
"妈妈说你讨厌上学 她走的时候你还哭了"
"Mummy says you hate it and cried when she left you."

118
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:10,440
"记住 你是我的至爱"
"Remember, I love you more than anybody.

119
00:05:10,520 --> 00:05:12,440
"姐妹 苏"
"Your sister, Suze."

120
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:15,720
- 她没寄出去 - 是的
- She never sent it? - No.

121
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:18,020
好吧 我们先去看看她的公寓
Okay, let's take a look at her flat.

122
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:24,720
查克斯 帮我查查斯蒂芬・博蒙特行吗
Chuks, run a check on Mr Stephen Beaumont, would you?

123
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:29,240
