I need money...quickly.

136
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:12,000
你在哪儿 哪个区域
Where are you? What part?

137
00:06:12,080 --> 00:06:14,840
我不知道 有个电话亭 红色的
I don't know. Phone box, it's red.

138
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:16,920
