There is a field with two horses.

139
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,480
房子什么颜色
And what colour are the horses?

140
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:20,760
有一栋是棕色的...
Um, there is one brown...

141
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:23,676
另一栋是黑的 带白色斑点
and the other one is black with white spots.

142
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:27,280
我开玩笑呢 亲爱的 你在哪条街
I'm joking, babe. What street are you on?

143
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:30,500
我... 我看不到任何标志 什么都没有
I... I can't see any signs, there's nothing.

144
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:34,440
无名街... 旁边有匹马
Where the streets have no name... near a horse.

145
00:06:34,520 --> 00:06:37,040
因为这样我才不常去乡下旅游
That's why I don't normally travel the countryside.

146
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:39,520
我想起来了 有个酒吧
I see, there is a pub.

147
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:41,480
我们经过一条路
We passed on the road.

148
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:43,520
叫狐狸和什么的
Um, the Fox and something.

149
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:45,800
猎犬
Hounds?

150
