弗金 黑尔
Firkin? Hare?

151
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:50,280
猎犬 还有那房子在路的同一边
Hounds, and the house is on the same side of the road,

152
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:52,320
有一点远
just a little bit further.

153
00:06:52,400 --> 00:06:54,200
好
Okay.

154
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:56,840
我会用导航仪在荒郊中心兜一圈的
I'll search through the middle of nowhere on my GPS.

155
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:58,864
玩一下午的猎狗追狐
An afternoon of playing Fox and Hounds

156
00:06:58,865 --> 00:07:01,240
把去伦敦的火车票给你
gets you a train ticket to London.

157
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:04,440
再给点零花钱去参观白金汉宫
Some extra pocket money to visit Buckingham Palace.

158
00:07:07,760 --> 00:07:09,080
我不明白为什么...
I don't know why...

159
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:12,831
我从没干过这个 不知道怎么...
I've never done this before, I don't know how...

160
00:07:12,840 --> 00:07:15,680
