569
00:33:22,120 --> 00:33:24,160
- 你们帮不了我 - 这没信号

570
00:33:24,320 --> 00:33:26,240
到外面去找信号

571
00:33:26,623 --> 00:33:29,474
给我们看你们的脸 给我们看你们的脸
Show us your face. Show us your face.

572
00:33:29,934 --> 00:33:31,774
或者离开这
Or get out of there.

573
00:33:31,854 --> 00:33:33,774
一定有人在监视你们
You know who else must be watching.

574
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:45,560
- 离开这 - 她去求助了

575
00:33:45,720 --> 00:33:47,280
我不能丢下你 先生

576
00:33:49,280 --> 00:33:51,200
莉亚在报警 会没事的

577
00:33:53,000 --> 00:33:54,240
天啊

578
00:34:13,520 --> 00:34:15,760
一个女孩失踪了 莉亚・马丁

579
00:34:15,920 --> 00:34:18,440
这夹克的样式和她妈妈描述的一样

580
00:34:18,600 --> 00:34:20,720
她和男朋友私奔了 西蒙・马西尔

581
00:34:21,560 --> 00:34:22,639
他们有电话吗

582
00:34:22,800 --> 00:34:25,720
他没有 她关机了所以她父亲找不到她

583
00:34:26,720 --> 00:34:29,719
我们搜查了他们的居住地并询问了他们的朋友

584
00:34:29,880 --> 00:34:32,560
继续搜查任何能让我们知道他们位置的消息

585
00:34:33,442 --> 00:34:35,042
两个孩子
Two kids?

586
00:34:38,702 --> 00:34:40,960
也许这会让真理杀手相形见绌
Maybe that will take the shine off the Truth Terrorist.

587
00:34:40,960 --> 00:34:43,159
还是联系不上他

588
00:34:43,602 --> 00:34:45,782
不好意思
Excuse me.

589
00:34:47,560 --> 00:34:49,159
也许他又换服务器了

590
00:34:49,840 --> 00:34:50,840
也许...

591
00:34:51,520 --> 00:34:53,480
他是很小心地策划这件事的

592
00:34:54,159 --> 00:34:55,599
不会轻易放弃的

593
00:35:19,862 --> 00:35:23,942
很好 你收到这个新电话了
Good, you received a new phone.

594
00:35:24,022 --> 00:35:25,662
你不想让警察听到
You don't want the cops listening.

595
00:35:25,742 --> 00:35:29,262
这是你和我之间的谈话
These conversations are just for you and me.

596
00:35:29,342 --> 00:35:30,702
我真是受宠若惊
I suppose I'm flattered.

597
00:35:32,502 --> 00:35:33,502
那么
So?

598
00:35:34,622 --> 00:35:36,822
你想让我把什么公布于众
What do you want me to tell the world?

599
00:35:36,902 --> 00:35:37,982
问我个问题
Ask me a question.

600
00:35:39,822 --> 00:35:40,822
好的
All right.

601
00:35:42,622 --> 00:35:44,422
信号断后发生了什么事
What happened when the feed went dead?

602
00:35:44,502 --> 00:35:47,702
其他人都是谁还有为什么你要挂断线
Who were the other people and why did you go offline?

603
00:35:47,782 --> 00:35:48,742
下个问题
Next question.

604
00:35:55,382 --> 00:35:57,142
那个人还活着吗
Is the man still alive?

605
00:35:57,222 --> 00:35:58,182
是的
Yes.

606
00:36:00,662 --> 00:36:03,102
为什么有五个真相
Why five truths?

607
00:36:03,182 --> 00:36:05,262
这之后你会停手吗
What, are you just going to stop after that?

608
00:36:05,342 --> 00:36:07,462
现在说这个还为时尚早
We are a long way from that point still.

609
00:36:10,462 --> 00:36:12,582
你到底想怎样
What do you want?

610
00:36:12,662 --> 00:36:14,102
你做这一切是为了什么
What is all this getting you?

611
00:36:14,182 --> 00:36:15,938
为了接近真相
Closer to the truth.

612
00:36:16,142 --> 00:36:19,632
我们都离真相越来越近了
We're all getting closer to the truth.

613
00:36:19,822 --> 00:36:22,982
那么...接下来你要做什么
So...what's next?

614
00:36:23,062 --> 00:36:25,262
我手里的那个老人还有救
The old man I'm holding can be saved.

615
00:36:26,422 --> 00:36:28,662
用你的报纸告诉大家
Use your newspaper to tell people that.

616
00:36:28,742 --> 00:36:31,182
他还有救
He can be saved.

617
00:36:31,262 --> 00:36:32,702
怎么救
How?

618
00:36:33,862 --> 00:36:36,382
怎么救
How?

619
00:36:56,022 --> 00:36:58,462
苏菲
hey, Sophie.

620
00:37:01,542 --> 00:37:02,542
最近怎么样
How's it going?

621
00:37:03,982 --> 00:37:05,422
还不错
Fine.

622
00:37:05,502 --> 00:37:06,462
很好
Good.

623
00:37:07,582 --> 00:37:08,902
我爸爸在吗
Is my dad here?

624
00:37:08,982 --> 00:37:09,992
他出海了
He had to go to sea,

625
00:37:09,993 --> 00:37:13,022
他...买了艘新船所以他...
he's, erm, got a new ship that he had to...

626
00:37:20,342 --> 00:37:21,742
我们去那边坐会
Come sit with me a minute.

627
00:37:24,262 --> 00:37:25,822
你不能每次和你妈妈吵架
You can't keep turning up like this

628
00:37:25,902 --> 00:37:27,782
都跑来我这里
every time you have a row with your mother.

629
00:37:27,862 --> 00:37:29,142
我们之间有监护的规定
There's a custody order.

630
00:37:29,222 --> 00:37:31,582
因为格蕾丝根本不想见到我
Because Grace doesn't want to see me.

631
00:37:31,662 --> 00:37:33,382
你要理解她
You have to understand her too.

632
00:37:33,462 --> 00:37:37,222
她觉得我更偏爱你
She feels I prefer you to the little ones.

633
00:37:37,302 --> 00:37:39,462
我喜欢那种感觉
I'd love to have that feeling.

634
00:37:40,662 --> 00:37:42,942
汤姆只有四岁
Tom's only four.

635
00:37:43,022 --> 00:37:44,422
洁米才九个月大
Jamie's only nine months.

636
00:37:44,502 --> 00:37:46,862
和他们比你是个大姑娘了 几乎是成人了
Compared to them you're a big girl. Almost a grown-up.

637
00:37:46,942 --> 00:37:48,422
我可以在这过夜
I can stay the night though,

638
00:37:48,502 --> 00:37:50,582
这不违反监护规定
that's not against the custody order.

639
00:37:51,262 --> 00:37:54,222
事实上 今晚是汤姆的生日宴会
The thing is, it's Tom's birthday party this evening

640
00:37:54,302 --> 00:37:57,062
并且格蕾丝一家人都要在这过夜
and Grace's family are all staying the night.

641
00:37:57,142 --> 00:37:58,182
我们没有多余的房间了
We don't have room.

642
00:38:00,422 --> 00:38:04,702
好啦 我知道你能处理好和你妈的关系
Come on, I know you can sort things out with your mother.

643
00:38:07,302 --> 00:38:08,902
需要我送你回去吗
You want me to drive you back?

644
00:38:15,742 --> 00:38:17,582
有什么需要就给我打电话 好吗
Call me if you need anything, eh?

645
00:38:22,182 --> 00:38:25,542
有个小男孩在牧场里玩
And there was a little boy in the field.

646
00:38:25,622 --> 00:38:28,782
他看上去很可爱 但不会说英语
Ever so sweet, he was. Didn't have a word of English.

647
00:38:28,862 --> 00:38:30,062
你说的妈妈是...
And you said the mum...?

648
00:38:30,142 --> 00:38:31,502
她非常奇怪
She was really strange.

649
00:38:31,582 --> 00:38:33,662
看上去好像有人刚打过她
And it looked as though someone had just hit her.

650
00:38:33,742 --> 00:38:35,942
之后 当我经过时 门是开着的
And later, when I walked past, the door was open

651
00:38:36,022 --> 00:38:37,542
但是没有人在那
but there was nobody there.

652
00:38:38,622 --> 00:38:40,382
我不想给他们找麻烦
I don't want to get them into trouble.

653
00:38:40,462 --> 00:38:41,942
"宽以待人"是我的格言
"Live and let live" is my motto.

654
00:38:42,022 --> 00:38:45,542
我也是  除非他们是托特纳姆的球迷
Mine too. Well, unless they're Tottenham.

655
00:38:45,622 --> 00:38:47,382
我真的很担心他们
I'm really worried about them.

656
00:38:47,462 --> 00:38:49,782
这不对劲 那里肯定发生了什么
It's just not right, what goes on in there.

657
00:39:28,182 --> 00:39:29,582
抱歉 姑娘 我们打烊了
Sorry, love, I'm closed.

658
00:40:00,942 --> 00:40:02,502
你站在那里做什么
Why are you standing there?

659
00:40:03,362 --> 00:40:05,062
关你什么事
What's it to you?

660
00:40:06,142 --> 00:40:08,142
你都湿透了 一定很冷
You look cold and wet.

661
00:40:08,842 --> 00:40:12,182
那是因为这雨天太冷了
That's because it's freezing and raining.

662
00:40:15,222 --> 00:40:16,902
你不能站在这里
You can't stand there.

663
00:40:19,642 --> 00:40:22,582
你脸上是雨水还是你在哭
Is that rain on your face or are you crying?

664
00:40:27,862 --> 00:40:30,622
我正准备泡杯茶
I was just about to have a cup of tea.

665
00:40:31,862 --> 00:40:34,982
如何你愿意 可以给你来一杯
There's enough for two if you want one.

666
00:40:39,902 --> 00:40:41,262
抱歉 姑娘
Sorry, love.

667
00:41:05,622 --> 00:41:06,822
放弃了吗
Given up, eh?

668
00:41:06,902 --> 00:41:09,022
- 进展如何 - 很好
- How's it going? - Good.

669
00:41:09,102 --> 00:41:11,782
虽然只工作了八年 但这次我确信
It's only been eight years but I'm confident this time.

670
00:41:11,862 --> 00:41:13,382
就我而言是五年
Five in my case.

671
00:41:13,462 --> 00:41:14,330
不错
Well done.

672
00:41:14,680 --> 00:41:15,680
孩子们有消息吗

673
00:41:16,396 --> 00:41:17,398
没有

674
00:41:19,800 --> 00:41:21,760
每次他有动作 我都能更了解他

675
00:41:23,040 --> 00:41:24,920
我已经开始明白他的规则了

676
00:41:26,400 --> 00:41:28,120
你觉得他遵守规则吗

677
00:41:28,902 --> 00:41:30,142
是的
Yes.

678
00:41:31,182 --> 00:41:33,102
我们都遵守规则
We all follow rules.

679
00:41:35,542 --> 00:41:37,542
那只狗和孩子们不在他的计划中
The dog and the kids he hadn't planned on.

680
00:41:37,622 --> 00:41:40,062
- 它抛弃了他 - 我知道他的感受
- It threw him. - I know how he feels.

681
00:41:40,142 --> 00:41:42,542
是啊 他让一个人又重操旧业了
Yeah. It'd drive a man back to cigarettes.

682
00:41:42,622 --> 00:41:45,502
你的法语有进步
Your French is getting better.

683
00:41:45,582 --> 00:41:48,022
- 谢谢 - 你要走吗
- Merci. - You're leaving?

684
00:41:48,102 --> 00:41:49,262
是的
Yep.

685
00:41:49,342 --> 00:41:51,242
我和你一起走
I'll come down with you.

686
00:41:52,080 --> 00:41:54,240
别一整晚盯在这 去睡会吧

687
00:41:57,602 --> 00:41:58,782
等我取下东西
I'll get my stuff.

688
00:42:00,822 --> 00:42:02,702
晚安
Bonne nuit.

689
00:42:06,122 --> 00:42:09,342
我受邀去巴黎工作 永久性的
I've been asked to go to Paris, permanently.

690
00:42:10,862 --> 00:42:14,502
比起加莱谁能不选择去巴黎
Well, who could possibly choose Paris over Calais?

691
00:42:16,582 --> 00:42:18,822
你喜欢爱丽丝
You like Elise?

692
00:42:18,902 --> 00:42:20,862
- 怎么看出来的 - 任何地方
- In what sense? - In any sense.

693
00:42:21,982 --> 00:42:23,782
她是个好警察
She's a good cop.

694
00:42:23,862 --> 00:42:26,302
是我合作过的最好的
Best I ever worked with.

695
00:42:26,382 --> 00:42:28,302
当然 不是谁都能理解她的
Not everybody gets her, of course.

696
00:42:29,182 --> 00:42:31,382
- 晚安 - 晚安
- Night. - Night.

697
00:42:31,462 --> 00:42:32,542
车不错
Nice car.

698
00:42:34,702 --> 00:42:37,262
恭喜你得到巴黎的工作
Congratulations on the Paris job.

699
00:42:37,342 --> 00:42:39,382
我还没有告诉爱丽丝
I haven't spoke to Elise about it yet.

700
00:42:39,462 --> 00:42:41,522
先别告诉任何人
Keep it to yourself for now.

701
00:43:02,982 --> 00:43:04,942
我这只有绿茶
I've only got green tea.

702
00:43:05,509 --> 00:43:07,448
很好了
That's great.

703
00:43:54,762 --> 00:43:57,082
你为什么哭
Why were you crying?

704
00:44:01,642 --> 00:44:03,222
家庭琐事
Family stuff.

705
00:44:05,522 --> 00:44:07,582
常有的事
That happens.

706
00:44:22,022 --> 00:44:24,462
我不能回家
I can't go home.

707
00:44:29,162 --> 00:44:31,462
如果你愿意就呆在这里
Stay here if you want.

708
00:44:31,542 --> 00:44:34,582
- 这里 - 你可以睡那边的床
- Here? - You can sleep on the bed in there.

709
00:44:34,962 --> 00:44:36,982
这只有一间卧室
There's only one bedroom.

710
00:44:37,062 --> 00:44:38,822
我可以睡我的瑜伽垫上
I sleep on my yoga mat.

711
00:44:40,422 --> 00:44:41,702
真的 你睡床吧
Really, take the bed.

712
00:44:42,842 --> 00:44:46,342
最近都没人用过所以床单很干净
It hasn't been used recently so the sheets are clean.

713
00:44:51,262 --> 00:44:54,402
也许我妈现在会有点失眠
Maybe my mum will lose a bit of sleep now.

714
00:45:15,822 --> 00:45:19,462
菲利普 菲利普
Philippe! Philippe!

715
00:45:28,920 --> 00:45:30,080
他很冷

716
00:45:31,182 --> 00:45:33,182
他又在线上了
He's back online.

717
00:45:37,062 --> 00:45:39,742
老人在冬天一般会怎样
What happens to old people in winter?

718
00:45:48,120 --> 00:45:48,760
{\an8}救他

719
00:45:56,600 --> 00:45:58,240
{\an8}他们能救他

